products.title: Shoe Covers
products.body_html:
SHOE COVERS from Uncut Packaging help prevent unwanted dust, dirt, and grime from being tracked into sensitive work areas. Uncut Packaging offers a wide selection of shoe covers that should be the perfect fit for your customers’ needs. Choose from our light weight disposable polyethylene shoe covers to our heavy weight rubber “nuke” boot. Our many varieties include non-skid options for added safety.

Product Features

  •  COLORS - BLUE, WHITE, CLEAR, YELLOW
  •  POLYPROPYLENE SHOE COVER WITH AND WITHOUT TREAD
  •  100% LATEX FREE
  •  SIZES - LG - 2X
  •  PACKED 200 - 300/CS (VARIES BASED ON PRODUCT)

products.title: Gloves - Chemical and Flock Lined Gloves
products.body_html:
CHEMICAL & FLOCK LINED GLOVES may be universally known as ‘that dish-washing glove’ but the uses (and varieties) extend beyond household cleaning. High volume food service (such as meat processing plants) benefit from an increased resistance to animal fats. For chemical protection, blended and nitrile gloves offer greater chemical resistance over standard latex. Also available is our premium chlorinated flock lined glove with a beaded cuff. For added chemical protection, use our heavy weight neoprene latex blended gloves. These gloves offer three different grip styles to choose from, raised diamond, recessed diamond and fish-scale. There are also three different kinds of cuffs, rolled, flat and pinked.

Product Features

  •  CHEMICAL & FLOCK LINED GLOVES
  •  11 - 40 MIL THICKNESS
  •  FISH SCALE GRIP, RECESSED DIAMOND AND RAISED DIAMOND
  •  ROLLED CUFF
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (12″)
  •  SMALL – EXTRA LARGE
  •  PACKED ONE PAIR PER BAG, 12 DZ/CS (144 PAIRS PER CASE)

products.title: Gloves - Polyethylene
products.body_html:
POLYETHYLENE GLOVES are our most economical glove. PE gloves are most often used for light duty tasks that require frequent glove changes. This glove has a loose fit design for easy on and off applications, and is especially useful in food service lines, deli counters, and other high volume applications. Uncut Packaging's clear PE Gloves are available in high density, low density, cast poly, and a new stretch hybrid version that is also available in blue. All PE gloves sold by Uncut Packaging are powder free and non-medical as well.

Product Features

  •  CLEAR POLYETHYLENE GLOVES
  •  POWDER FREE
  •  EMBOSSED GRIP
  •  DIE CUT & HEAT SEALED EDGES
  •  AVAILABLE IN LOW AND HIGH DENSITY, CAST POLY AND STRETCH HYBRID
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (11.75″ +/- 0.25″)
  •  SMALL – EXTRA LARGE
  •  PACKED 100/BX 10BX/CARTON 10CARTONS/CS (10,000/MASTER CASE TOTAL)

products.title: Medical Grade Latex - 6 Mil Gloves
products.body_html:
LATEX GLOVES from Uncut Packaging provide the best feel, fit and dexterity. Our gloves are available in both lightly powdered and powder free options in a variety of thicknesses. Our lightly powdered latex gloves are produced with a food grade corn starch powder, making donning easier especially when hands are wet. Powder free gloves go through an extra process of chlorinating the gloves to ease donning. Our polymer coated latex gloves provide an additional barrier to prevent latex proteins from touching the skin.

Product Features

  •  NATURAL LATEX GLOVES
  •  MEDICAL GRADE / Exam Grade
  •  POWDER FREE
  • TEAR RESISTANT
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (9.65″ +/- 0.25″)
  •  SMALL – EXTRA LARGE
  •  NATURAL COLOR - PACKED 100/BX 10BX/CS (1,000 PCS/CS TOTAL)
  •  12" BLUE COLOR - PACKED 50/BX 10BX/CS (500 PCS/CS TOTAL)

products.title: Gloves - Powder Free Natural Latex - 6 Mil
products.body_html:
6 Mil LATEX GLOVES from Uncut Packaging provide the best feel, fit and dexterity. Our gloves are available in both lightly powdered and powder free options in a variety of thicknesses. Our lightly powdered latex gloves are produced with a food grade corn starch powder, making donning easier especially when hands are wet. Powder free gloves go through an extra process of chlorinating the gloves to ease donning. Our polymer coated latex gloves provide an additional barrier to prevent latex proteins from touching the skin.

Product Features

  •  NATURAL LATEX GLOVES
  •  POWDER FREE
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (9.65″ +/- 0.25″)
  •  EXTRA SMALL – 2X LARGE
  • FDA Medical / Exam Grade
  •  PACKED 100/BX 10BX/CS (1,000 PCS/CS TOTAL)

products.title: Gloves - Powdered Nitrile Gloves
products.body_html:
POWDERED NITRILE GLOVES are the perfect compromise between latex and vinyl. Nitrile is made from an allergy safe compound that feels a lot like latex but it’s much stronger, costs less, and is more comfortable to wear. Powdered Nitrile is perfect for demanding applications. Our powdered versions are produced with a food grade corn starch powder, making it easier to take them on or off – especially with wet hands. 


Product Features

  •  MFG#: GNDR-(SIZE)-1M
  •  BLUE NITRILE GLOVES
  •  POWDERED
  •  100% LATEX FREE
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (9.65″ +/- 0.25″)
  •  SMALL – EXTRA LARGE
  •  PACKED 100/BX 10BX/CS (1,000 PCS/CS TOTAL)

products.title: Nitrile Gloves - 5 Mil
products.body_html:
5 MIL NITRILE GLOVES are the perfect compromise between latex and vinyl. Nitrile is made from an allergy safe compound that feels a lot like latex but it’s much stronger, costs less, and is more comfortable to wear. Nitrile is perfect for demanding applications, especially cleaning and dishwashing. Uncut Packaging's lightly powdered versions are produced with a food grade corn starch powder, making it easier to take them on or off – especially with wet hands.

Product Features 

  •  BLUE NITRILE GLOVES
  • FDA MEDICAL / EXAM GRADE
  •  POWDER FREE
  •  100% LATEX FREE
  •  STANDARD LENGTH (9.65″ +/- 0.25″)
  •  SMALL – 2X LARGE
